00:34.940 --> 00:37.340
<i>When I was a little girl,</i>

00:37.340 --> 00:39.460
<i>my mother would remind me
each night before bed</i>

00:39.460 --> 00:44.060
<i>to open up my heart to God, 
for he was kind,merciful and just.</i>

00:44.940 --> 00:47.420
<i>Things changed when my
father left a few years later...</i>

00:47.420 --> 00:52.140
<i>leaving her to raise me and my brothers in a little place
on the edge of the Mojave Desert.</i>

00:52.220 --> 00:55.780
<i>She never talked of a
kind, merciful God again.</i>

00:56.540 --> 00:59.420
<i>Instead she spoke of a prophecy....</i>

00:59.420 --> 01:01.940
<i>Of a time when all the world
would be covered in darkness,</i>

01:01.940 --> 01:04.500
<i>and the fate of mankind
would be decided.</i>

01:04.700 --> 01:07.100
<i>One night I finally got up
the courage to ask my mother</i>

01:07.100 --> 01:11.500
<i>Why God had changed?
Why he was so mad at his children?</i>

01:12.800 --> 01:17.480
<i>"I don't know," she said,
tucking the covers around me.</i>

01:17.880 --> 01:21.400
<i>"I guess he just got tired
of all the bullshit."</i>

04:22.480 --> 04:25.760
Goddamn animals.

04:25.760 --> 04:32.080
In nights like this I'd like to take a match to this city so 
I could watch all these motherfuckers burn.

04:32.080 --> 04:34.760
Just a good ol' boy barbecue, eh?

04:34.760 --> 04:39.360
A fresh start. 
That’s what this place needs.

05:04.200 --> 05:07.680
Stop! Drop the bags,
put your hands on your head!

05:12.760 --> 05:15.160
It’s starting.

05:15.160 --> 05:18.680
There isn’t much time.

05:18.680 --> 05:23.400
Shut the fuck up and drop the bags now!

05:24.840 --> 05:28.000
Hands on your head!
On your head!

05:29.440 --> 05:33.280
Turn around! 
Turn the fuck around!

05:42.200 --> 05:44.880
Let him go!

05:44.880 --> 05:46.800
Let him fuck...

05:55.520 --> 05:57.640
Burton!

06:00.120 --> 06:04.560
What are you doing, Michael?
These weren't your orders.

06:04.560 --> 06:06.840
What is he saying?

06:06.840 --> 06:09.320
No, I'm following my own orders now.

06:09.360 --> 06:12.320
Then you will die along with the child.

06:12.320 --> 06:16.040
Burton, you fucking know this guy?
What the hell is...

07:28.620 --> 07:30.540
You okay, Jeep?

07:32.060 --> 07:35.420
Sorry I woke you, Charlie.
-Yeah. 

07:36.220 --> 07:38.580
Wasn't you.

07:38.620 --> 07:41.580
He's been kicking up a storm all night.

07:41.580 --> 07:44.460
Must know something I don't.

07:54.820 --> 07:56.900
Another bad dream?

07:59.700 --> 08:02.860
It's just stress, Jeep, that's all.

08:04.500 --> 08:07.100
