08:16.300 --> 08:19.660
You're the only thing I
like to worry about.

08:20.660 --> 08:22.900
See what I mean?

08:22.900 --> 08:26.220
You're worried about a girl that's eight months pregnant,
and it isn't your baby.

08:27.180 --> 08:29.860
