14:32.840 --> 14:34.920
Hey, man, you got a phone I can use?

14:34.920 --> 14:37.920
My cell phone ain't got no reception,
and the phone booth outside is busted. 

14:37.920 --> 14:40.880
Excuse me, is there any news about 
when our car might be fixed?

14:40.880 --> 14:42.320
You said your boy would have us back

14:42.320 --> 14:44.240
on the road two hours ago.
And I gotta say this...

14:44.440 --> 14:48.120
The rate we're going, we'll be lucky
to make it to Scottsdale by Christmas.

14:54.560 --> 14:59.840
Hey?! Hood's up on this beamer.
That mean anything to you?

14:59.840 --> 15:01.479
Yeah.

15:01.480 --> 15:05.880
