damned thing in another county,

17:00.500 --> 17:03.660
and I looked pretty damn stupid.

17:05.740 --> 17:08.660
And I see you making
the same damn mistake I made.

17:08.660 --> 17:11.859
Believing in something that's
never going to happen.

17:13.300 --> 17:18.220
You listen to me, son. It's
time for you to leave here.

17:18.220 --> 17:21.819
I don't want to see you wake up one day

17:21.819 --> 17:25.380
old and pissed off, realizing you're lost,

17:25.380 --> 17:28.339
just like everybody else
that stops here.

17:33.060 --> 17:35.740
Go on. Fix the car.

17:36.840 --> 17:39.360
I want these people out
of here by nightfall.

17:45.680 --> 17:48.120
He's about this close
to wrapping it up.

18:17.520 --> 18:19.640
