to talk to his son, that’s why.

20:01.620 --> 20:07.140
I don't care what your lawyer said, I got my own lawyer,
now put him on the god damn phone.

20:08.340 --> 20:10.260
Hello?

20:10.460 --> 20:13.060
Your phone is breaking
up, do you hear me?

20:15.580 --> 20:17.500
Shit.

20:21.940 --> 20:25.100
